  SECTION 3 — EXTRACT DIFFERENCE
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════
{%- endcomment -%}

<section class="sbp-section sbp-section--base sbp-spagyric" id="SbpSpagyric">
  <div class="sbp-container sbp-spagyric__grid">

    <div class="sbp-spagyric__content">
      <span class="sb-eyebrow">The Extraction Advantage</span>
      <h2 class="sbp-section-headline">Why juice extracts and not powders.</h2>
      <p class="sbp-spagyric__body">Most turmeric products use dried powder. We use juice extracts — a concentrated form that preserves a broader range of the plant's active compounds than standard drying can. Turmeric's curcumin is notoriously poorly absorbed on its own. We pair it with black pepper extract containing piperine, which research shows can enhance curcumin absorption by up to 2000%.</p>
      <p class="sbp-spagyric__body">We also include ginger juice extract — traditionally used for digestive comfort, circulation, and nausea support, and itself a potent supporter of the body's inflammatory pathways.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="sbp-spagyric__callout">
      <div class="sbp-callout-box">
        <div class="sbp-callout-box__icon">⚗</div>
        <p class="sbp-callout-box__text">"The difference between a turmeric latte that tastes nice and one that actually does something is in the extraction method and the bioavailability stack. Golden Latte is built for the latter."</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

{%- comment -%}
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════
  SECTION 4 — INGREDIENT GROUPS ACCORDION
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════
{%- endcomment -%}

<section class="sbp-section sbp-section--card sbp-ingredients" id="SbpIngredients">
  <div class="sbp-container">

    <div class="sbp-ingredients__header">
      <span class="sb-eyebrow">What's Inside</span>
      <h2 class="sbp-section-headline">Six ingredient groups. One governing idea.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="sbp-accordion-grid">

      <details class="sbp-accordion__item" open>
        <summary class="sbp-accordion__trigger">
          <span class="sbp-accordion__num">01</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__label">Sprouted Greens</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__caret"><svg width="12" height="8" viewBox="0 0 12 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 1L6 6L11 1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="sbp-accordion__body">
          <p class="sbp-accordion__ingredients">Alfalfa Sprouts · Broccoli Sprouts</p>
          <p class="sbp-accordion__copy">Broccoli sprouts are one of the most potent natural sources of sulforaphane — a compound well-researched for its role in activating Nrf2, the body's master antioxidant and detoxification pathway. Alfalfa sprouts contribute enzymes, chlorophyll, and additional phytonutrients. Sprouting increases the bioavailability of these compounds beyond what mature vegetables can provide.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="sbp-accordion__item">
        <summary class="sbp-accordion__trigger">
          <span class="sbp-accordion__num">02</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__label">The Extract Duo</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__caret"><svg width="12" height="8" viewBox="0 0 12 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 1L6 6L11 1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="sbp-accordion__body">
          <p class="sbp-accordion__ingredients">Turmeric Juice Extract · Ginger Juice Extract</p>
          <p class="sbp-accordion__copy">These are not powders. Juice extracts preserve a broader range of the plant's active compounds than standard dried powder at a higher concentration. Turmeric's curcumin is one of the most extensively studied natural compounds for supporting a healthy inflammatory response. Ginger complements it — traditionally used for digestive comfort, circulation, and nausea support.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="sbp-accordion__item">
        <summary class="sbp-accordion__trigger">
          <span class="sbp-accordion__num">03</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__label">8-Mushroom Blend</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__caret"><svg width="12" height="8" viewBox="0 0 12 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 1L6 6L11 1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="sbp-accordion__body">
          <p class="sbp-accordion__ingredients">Chaga · Maitake · Reishi · Royal Agaricus · Shiitake · Turkey Tail · Cordyceps · Lion's Mane</p>
          <p class="sbp-accordion__copy">Eight of the most revered medicinal mushrooms in traditional and modern functional medicine in a single serving. Turkey Tail and Chaga are among the most researched for immune-modulating beta-glucans. Maitake supports metabolic health. Shiitake contributes to cardiovascular wellness. Royal Agaricus is associated with immune support. Together this blend covers the entire spectrum of mushroom-supported wellness — immunity, cognition, energy, cellular health, and adaptability to stress.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="sbp-accordion__item">
        <summary class="sbp-accordion__trigger">
          <span class="sbp-accordion__num">04</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__label">Bioavailability Stack</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__caret"><svg width="12" height="8" viewBox="0 0 12 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 1L6 6L11 1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="sbp-accordion__body">
          <p class="sbp-accordion__ingredients">Black Pepper Extract (Piperine)</p>
          <p class="sbp-accordion__copy">Piperine is proven to enhance curcumin absorption by up to 2000% — which is why it is non-negotiable in any serious turmeric formula. Without it most of the curcumin you consume passes through without being absorbed. With it the entire formula becomes dramatically more effective.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="sbp-accordion__item">
        <summary class="sbp-accordion__trigger">
          <span class="sbp-accordion__num">05</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__label">Warming Spices</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__caret"><svg width="12" height="8" viewBox="0 0 12 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 1L6 6L11 1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="sbp-accordion__body">
          <p class="sbp-accordion__ingredients">Carob · Cinnamon · Cardamom</p>
          <p class="sbp-accordion__copy">Each chosen for function beyond flavor. Cinnamon supports healthy blood sugar metabolism. Cardamom supports digestion and adds a beautiful aromatic warmth. Carob provides a natural caffeine-free depth of flavor that makes Golden Latte genuinely luxurious to drink.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

      <details class="sbp-accordion__item">
        <summary class="sbp-accordion__trigger">
          <span class="sbp-accordion__num">06</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__label">Why Caffeine-Free Matters</span>
          <span class="sbp-accordion__caret"><svg width="12" height="8" viewBox="0 0 12 8" fill="none"><path d="M1 1L6 6L11 1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg></span>
        </summary>
        <div class="sbp-accordion__body">
          <p class="sbp-accordion__copy">Golden Latte contains no caffeine — making it suitable as an afternoon or evening ritual, or for people who prefer to avoid caffeine entirely. The energy you feel from Golden Latte comes from mushroom adaptogenic support and inflammatory balance, not stimulation. It is sustainable and calm.</p>
        </div>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

